niagara.utils
Class ArrayStack

java.lang.Object
  niagara.utils.ArrayStack

public class ArrayStack
extends java.lang.Object

Definition of class ArrayStack . Just a stack implemented using an array. Wrote this because the ArrayList class from java is too slow. The allocation of a ListIterator in the equals and hashCode functions is too expensive!!

Version:
1.0
Author:
Kristin Tufte
